# Tauri dev-mode file watcher ignores everything below. Same syntax as
# .gitignore. Without this, Tauri detects every rebuild of the Swift
# biometric sidecar binary in `binaries/` as a source change and triggers
# yet another rebuild — an infinite loop the moment the dev server starts.

# The Swift sidecar output. build.rs rewrites this on every cargo run.
binaries/

# Quarantined cortex artifacts that might accidentally land under src-tauri
# during local debugging. Should never normally appear here.
*.corrupt-*
